TU Wien publication fund https://www.tuwien.at/bibliothek/forschen-und-publizieren/foerderungen
Requirements open access gold
aubmitting autor from tu vienna
article appears in open access journal from this list: https://www.doaj.org/
costs are not covered by other funds (FWF)
The publication fee for the article does not exceed EUR 2000. Higher costs can be assumed in individual cases.
TU Wien Bibliothek must be mentioned in the acknowledgements

Gold open access journals from the list:
=====================================
Journal of Optimization
https://www.hindawi.com/journals/jopti/
APC $1025
submit by one autor online as Only electronic PDF (.pdf) or Word (.doc, .docx, .rtf) files, no page limit
article will be peer reviewed
preprints on preprint servers are possible
Formatting requirements:
Title and Authorship Information, Affiliations, Abstract, Introduction,Materials and Methods, Publishing Protocols.,Results and Discussion,Main Text (Review only), Conclusions, Data Availability, Conflicts of Interest, Funding Statement, Acknowledgments, References

=====================================
Logical Methods in Computer Science
https://lmcs.episciences.org/

=====================================
Journal of Algorithms & Computational Technology
https://journals.sagepub.com/home/act
H index 13

is a peer-reviewed open access journal which focusses on the employment of mathematical and numerical methods and computational technology in the development of engineering solutions or computational analysis.

This journal is a member of the Committee on Publication Ethics (COPE). https://publicationethics.org/about/our-organisation

The acceptance of papers is judged on the use of mathematical techniques and/or engineering methodology in the computational analysis and simulations of complex industrial and real life problems in the above areas

=====================================
Operations Research Perspectives
https://www.journals.elsevier.com/operations-research-perspectives/
H index 16, CiteScore: 4.3, Source Normalized Impact per Paper (SNIP): 1.648
OAPF USD 1750 for Research papers

Authorship of the Paper
Authorship should be limited to those who have made a significant contribution to the conception, design, execution, or interpretation of the reported study.  All those who have made substantial contributions should be listed as co-authors.

Alertness to Ethical Issues
A reviewer should be alert to potential ethical issues in the paper  and should bring these to the attention of the editor, including any substantial similarity or overlap between the manuscript under consideration and any other published paper of which the reviewer has personal knowledge. Any statement that an observation, derivation, or argument had been previously reported should be accompanied by the relevant citation.

dissemination of the research outputs
1 Social Media, such as Facebook, LinkedIn, Twitter via share links
2 On my institutional repository for gold open access
3 On a preprint server
4 At a conference You can always present your research in forms such as a presentation, or poster.

